## Description

This is a simple GTFS feed provided by Google for testing and demonstration purposes.
It contains sample transit data including:

- Agency information
- Stops
- Routes
- Trips
- Stop times
- Calendar data

The feed is used in our test suite to verify the gtfs-sqljs library works correctly with real GTFS data.
